THE DECISION OF 18 OCTOBER 1972 IS HEREBY AMENDED TO READ AS FOLLOWS :
1 . IN ANNEX I , THE LIST OF MILK PRODUCTS COVERED BY THE SURVEY IS REPLACED BY THE LIST APPEARING IN ANNEX I TO THIS DECISION ;
2 . IN ANNEX II , THE MODELS OF THE INFORMATION TABLES ARE REPLACED BY THE MODELS APPEARING IN ANNEX II TO THIS DECISION .
